        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[Polygon 联合创办人 Jaynti Kanani 退出团队！MATIC 下跌 3%]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">After kickstarting Polygon in 2017, around 6 months back, I decided to step back from the day-to-day grind.</p><p>I'm more confident in Polygon's bright future and passionate community. I'll be focusing on new adventures while still cheering and contributing to Polygon from the…</p><p>— Jaynti Kanani (JD) (@jdkanani) <a href="https://twitter.com/jdkanani/status/1709569503099519296?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 4, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2>Polygon 联合创办人 Jaynti Kanani 退出团队</h2><p>Polygon 联合创办人 Jaynti Kanani 昨日 (4) 晚间于 X (前身为 Twitter) 表示：「在 2017 年推出 Polygon 后，大约在 6 个月前，我决定退出日常工作。我对 Polygon 光明的未来和充满激情的社群更有信心，我将专注于新的冒险，同时仍然在幕后为 Polygon 加油并做出贡献。」</p><p>对于此消息，社群成员们一致给出了祝福的留言，另一位 Polygon 联合创办人 Sandeep Nailwal 也表示：「让我们持续推动 Polygon 向前行，不论是在内部还是外部都无关紧要。」</p><p>根据 CoinMarketCap 的<a href="https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/polygon/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">数据</a>，Jaynti 的退出对 MATIC 的价格似乎造成小幅影响，消息曝光后，MATIC 价格从 0.58 美元下跌至 0.56 美元，跌幅约 3%。</p><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-80222 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2023-10-05-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8810.43.31.png?resize=1045%2C529&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1045" height="529" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-05-上午 10.43.31.png?w=1045&amp;ssl=1 1045w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-05-上午 10.43.31.png?resize=300%2C152&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-05-上午 10.43.31.png?resize=1024%2C518&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-05-上午 10.43.31.png?resize=600%2C304&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截图-2023-10-05-上午 10.43.31.png?resize=768%2C389&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
]]>
            </description>
